column2: SELECT  all  s.SpecObjID,  s.objTypeName,  s.z,  s.mag_#, s.mag_#, s.mag_#, L.sigma,  L.height,  L.nSigma, P.specClass, P.type, P.objtype, P.dered_u, P.dered_g, P.dered_r, P.dered_i, dered_z into mydb.HaInclMorph FROM SpecObjAll as s   JOIN SpecLine as L ON s.SpecObjID = L.specObjID   JOIN SpecPhotoAll as P ON P.SpecObjID = L.specObjID WHERE L.LineId = # and s.zwarning = # and s.specClass = #
